Class Electronics

  • java.lang.Object
    • coe528.Electronics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MainStore

    public class Electronics
extends java.lang.Object
implements MainStore
    OVERVIEW: Grocery is mutable. It is specified by type, name, year, daysMin, daysMax price, and fastShip

    Abstraction Function: AF(c) = c.getName() | Name specifies what items name (ex apples)

    Rep Invariant: fastShip = true (comes arrives faster), false (arrives slower)
